Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:57.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Hello! Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm Minori Suzuki, the voice of Ena Shinonome from Nightcord at 25:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:13.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This ProSeka AfterTalk is a program where we look back on the event while sharing the messages we've received from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Today, we're covering the Colors of Pure Sense event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Did everyone enjoy the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Between the fan festa and the movie stage greetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:30.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,the real-life cast events have been quite busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But right after that, we have this Niigo event, Ena's story event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's been a bit of a whirlwind for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I hope you've been enjoying it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:49.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We were collecting letters for the AfterTalk via the official ProSeka Discord and email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you all for your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:56.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm so curious that I almost want to ask the staff to let me see all of them secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm really interested in what you all thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:04.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll be introducing some of the letters we received during the show, so please look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:11.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Also, please post your thoughts on the event or this broadcast using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm also watching the YouTube chat, so if you have any comments,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.93,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll be picking up the ones that catch my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:18.61,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Like, "It was a great story," and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I see "Little Niigo" in the chat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes, Little Niigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:30.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And today, we have the AfterLive at 10:00 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:37.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and the 3DMV for this event will be released at 10:05 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to watch that with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:48.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So, while I want to stick to the schedule, I also want to spend a bit more time watching the story videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:53.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was a bit selfish and asked for the story segments to be longer than usual today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I hope you'll enjoy watching them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:04.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, let's get right into talking about the story
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,of Colors of Pure Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,How did you all like the story this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:14.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's look back on it together while reading your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:19.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This is actually my first time doing the ProSeka AfterTalk since it was renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's been about a year, and back then it was before the renewal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:30.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so this is my first time doing the segment where I weave words together from your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm quite excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:35.16,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,This letter is from Amelia Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.82,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"They wrote, "This is my first time sending in my thoughts.""
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:43.98,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The scene that left an impression on me was when Ena deleted her selfie account."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:50.24,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I felt her growth when Ena, who used to run away from her art, finally decided to face it head-on."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:55.86,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Like Ena, I was also afraid of facing myself and kept running away,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:59.06,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but seeing Ena's positive attitude gave me the push I needed,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.96,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and made me want to do my best too."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:07.44,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ms. Suzuki, what kind of feelings did you put into your performance of Ena this time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.32,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:15.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Amelia Time, thank you for such a lovely message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:22.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk more about it while watching the story later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:42.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Something I was conscious of as Ena's voice actress, both in this event and when singing recent Niigo songs, was the resolve to not go back to the old Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I personally kept that in mind because,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,even if the pace is slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:14:04.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ena is moving forward bit by bit. Niigo's music often has negative lyrics or a dark atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,due to the nature of the unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:16.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I tried not to get pulled too far into that. Adding a nuance of tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:24.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,or negativity might make a line or a phrase stand out more to the listeners' ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and make them think, "Oh, I like this part" or "I want to hear that again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:33.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There are definitely things that catch the ear that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:38.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But that would just be my own desire for validation as Suzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:48.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I wanted to make sure Ena's gradual forward progress was reflected in both the songs and the dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:53.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even with the same words, I wanted to make sure you could feel that she's moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:15:06.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was conscious of that, and I gradually increased that level of positivity based on the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:11.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's what I kept in mind while performing this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:23.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,In this event and recent songs, she's realized that the world is warmer than she thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:28.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and she knows that the people around her will support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.66,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I made sure to reflect that in my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll introduce another letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.98,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,This one is from Sudachi Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.42,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Hello, Minori-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.98,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I watched Colors of Pure Sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.88,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"What left an impression on me was the scene in Episode 7 where Ena"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:58.30,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"gets so excited because she's having so much fun painting."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:04.28,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ena, who could only raise her self-esteem through others' evaluations, like selfies,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:11.02,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"finally realized, 'I'm fine just as I am. My world and my expression can be as free as I want them to be.'"
Comment: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:16.16,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:16.16,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ena's world is gradually becoming more colorful, and seeing her eyes sparkle"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:22.08,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"as she says drawing is fun... I could really feel that through your voice, Suzuki-san,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.30,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and it moved me to tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:30.28,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I want to continue watching over and supporting Ena, who has resolved not to give up on her art and her dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:34.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,From Niyori-san... "Ena's heart's color..." Oh, what a lovely message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:41.78,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for saying that my vocal performance brought it to life so vividly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thanking you for receiving it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:53.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I always hope that Ena's feelings will reach everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:58.74,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Of course, she's a game character, a 2D being,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but Ena is truly alive. And since no one knows
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:06.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,what her future holds yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I want to deliver something that feels real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:18.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for such a kind message. It makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.57,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:29.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have so much to talk about. If I keep chatting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll run out of time in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So let's move right along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've picked out some scenes I personally want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so let's watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:44.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was a bit selfish today with the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The staff are shaking their heads when I say "selfish," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I really struggled to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:48.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I honestly wanted to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,from episode 1 to 8 with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:54.90,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:18:00.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,let's look at episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:05.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This is an AfterTalk, so I'll be talking quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If you find me too noisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:14.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,please go back and watch the story in the game later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.83,0:33:35.57,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.57,0:33:36.33,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.33,0:33:37.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:39.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think she knew deep down all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.20,0:33:42.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's deleting her account... she's not hacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.80,0:33:47.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ena has made so many resolutions, but... wait, what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.64,0:33:48.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,With her selfie account,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:56.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,she used it as a way to escape or rely on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.20,0:33:57.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.72,0:34:00.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But she couldn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:01.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She wants to go to the exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.56,0:34:05.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But she didn't have the resolve to tell those around her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.76,0:34:06.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She acted like
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.16,0:34:11.36,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,it wasn't a big deal, but this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.88,0:34:18.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,she's actually quitting and making a real decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:31.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's painful from here on, but it feels like the fog in her heart has cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.96,0:34:37.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I acted this out with a mix of relief and the weight of what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.84,0:34:49.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,In the end, I felt like Ena was finally at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.12,0:35:03.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The reason I chose episodes 7 and 8 is because of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.80,0:35:11.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,They've been through a lot, and there were times she couldn't face him, but she really admires him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.45,0:35:26.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As she hit puberty and things happened, and since her dad isn't great with words, she ended up hiding her respect for him out of frustration. But as she grew as an artist, she remembered those feelings. 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.22,0:35:31.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's why I got to voicing young Ena was so special. As a child, she was so pure, and everything was new and sparkling. Her father was in that world,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:39.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As a child, she was so pure, and everything was new and sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:49.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And in that world was her father, and he was someone she looked up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:52.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Someone who creates amazing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:36:00.91,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I imagined Ena talking to him as just this mass of pure light.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.91,0:36:14.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I played that scene keeping in mind that feeling of wonder and delight Ena had for her father and the art he created.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.62,0:36:23.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And because of that, I could continue back into Ena's drawing scene keeping that same wonderful and sparkling feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.22,0:36:37.36,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Being able to draw with so much joy while embracing that feeling was a huge moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:41.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And for the first time, she could clearly say, "It's fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:47.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This is such an important point for Ena to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.54,0:36:50.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's still on her journey, but she finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.32,0:36:53.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:59.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And so when— Ah, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.68,0:37:06.05,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the script at home, I cried so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.05,0:37:07.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was just so happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.54,0:37:10.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Wah! This is a total broadcast accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.42,0:37:17.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's been five years—well, not five years in Ena's timeline—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.04,0:37:19.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but there's so been so much building up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.12,0:37:24.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think many of you find Ena's story very relatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.84,0:37:33.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Since I'm also in a world of art where there are no "correct" answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.15,0:37:34.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I really understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:45.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But more than that, seeing Ena's hard work finally start to pay off... well, "pay off" is a simple way to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.20,0:37:46.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.16,0:37:59.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was so happy that I cried for her as Minori Suzuki, thinking "Congratulations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:04.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And while reading, I felt Ena's relief that she finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.48,0:38:14.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She could finally feel a simple emotion. That tension she's been carrying finally snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.36,0:38:17.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry... I have plenty of tissues here.
Comment: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:23.64,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:23.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I put those feelings into it and the tears just started flowing naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.64,0:38:29.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There were parts where I got choked up and couldn't get the words out, but that's what acting is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.28,0:38:35.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If I'm crying as Ena, then the character on screen is crying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.82,0:38:39.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Since I was crying as Ena, she was crying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.52,0:38:47.49,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Usually, the dialogue moves forward with a button press, but they adjusted to my timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:57.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,They didn't cut the recording and cherished every moment until the button was pressed. I'm so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.54,0:39:10.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've received so many comments saying this was a great story. And it wasn't just about how my acting was,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.10,0:39:12.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,or how my voice sounded as Suzuki Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:27.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Instead of focusing on me, everyone really took Ena's way of life to heart. Some felt encouraged to work hard too,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.38,0:39:33.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and long-time fans were just so happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.12,0:39:45.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even though her journey is just beginning, I'm so glad people felt so much for Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.00,0:39:54.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I poured my absolute all into Ena for this, so I'm really happy with how it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.58,0:39:55.43,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.43,0:39:56.07,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.26,0:39:58.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, let's take a look at the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.56,0:40:07.05,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,By the way, I chose this one because it's the moment Ena finally sees a glimmer of hope after suffering for her art.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:07.75,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.34,0:40:15.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's spend about four minutes looking at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.18,0:40:22.98,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,Before that, I have some comments from the illustration team about the costumes to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.98,0:40:34.38,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The theme of this story is Ena's struggle to get into art school, nearly giving up after falling short,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.38,0:40:37.52,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but ultimately deciding not to quit."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:41.52,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The motif is an art apron over a school uniform,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:45.42,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"designed to capture Ena's look as a student preparing for entrance exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:48.80,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"While she has other apron outfits, for this event, we gave Ena a patched-up apron."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.80,0:40:52.64,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This represents her persistence through repeated setbacks."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.64,0:40:57.10,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's a unique arrangement for this specific story."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:41:00.14,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We kept strong uniform elements like the sailor collar and pleats,"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.14,0:41:06.16,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but modified the shape to give it more of a costume feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.16,0:41:09.92,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's the design philosophy behind it."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.92,0:41:12.66,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,And here is the illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.02,0:41:18.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The pre-trained version... everyone gave such great feedback on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.96,0:41:22.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She looks like she's having fun painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.50,0:41:23.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Her hands are all messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.78,0:41:25.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.30,0:41:34.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And here are the pre-trained and post-trained versions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.22,0:41:36.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,featuring everyone who watched over and supported Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:43.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Kanade is a creator herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.22,0:41:47.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so even though their genres are different, she understands Ena's feelings. And KAITO...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.80,0:41:54.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, KAITO gave Ena so many important words of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.94,0:42:01.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,They're all eating ice cream together. I named this one "Yogurt Ice Cream."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.38,0:42:04.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's just because I personally love yogurt ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:06.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's all about me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.14,0:42:07.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And here's Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.76,0:42:08.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.62,0:42:11.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Lovely, there are so many drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:13.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's eating ice cream too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.04,0:42:13.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Look, ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.01,0:42:15.51,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.54,0:42:19.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And finally, Mafu— wait, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.38,0:42:22.49,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't get the long-press to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:23.07,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.62,0:42:25.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's holding the apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.14,0:42:26.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes, adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.18,0:42:29.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:34.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So, you've seen the pre-trained and post-trained illustrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.94,0:42:36.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! How many times am I going to mess this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.30,0:42:38.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, those were the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.58,0:42:45.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I have a few more minutes, so I'll talk a bit more about the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.42,0:42:50.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The previous story wasn't specifically about her art,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.70,0:42:52.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but the one before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.62,0:42:54.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,where I sang the song "I am Rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.82,0:43:01.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,During that story about Ena's painting—I don't like saying "drawings."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.98,0:43:05.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, during that story, I happened to visit an art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.60,0:43:12.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was able to act while reflecting on what it means to look at a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.62,0:43:19.90,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It helped me understand Ena better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.90,0:43:24.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This time, I was just walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.72,0:43:31.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and I passed an actual art prep school, the kind Ena would attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.98,0:43:46.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I felt this intense tension just looking from the outside, and it reminded me how tough her world is before I went into recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.34,0:43:57.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I try to act every day in a way that conveys the reality of the place Ena is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.62,0:43:58.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.41,0:43:59.97,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.97,0:44:02.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.88,0:44:03.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.64,0:44:07.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I still have a few dozen seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:13.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Some of you might have already seen the AfterLive by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.02,0:44:16.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It follows the content of Episode 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.16,0:44:22.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so you can see Ena's refreshed expression. Things will still be hard for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.52,0:44:27.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I hope her resolve comes through in her expression and her singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:34.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I hope it's reaching all of you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.95,0:44:35.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:44:35.97,0:44:36.47,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.97,0:44:36.47,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.24,0:44:39.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Man, it really is a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.18,0:44:41.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ena is so loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.58,0:44:43.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful we got such a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:50.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,With that said, I'd like to talk about the music after we watch the 3DMV that was written specifically for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.18,0:44:51.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.88,0:45:11.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Breathing inside a borrowed life, in a body that can't become anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.12,0:45:21.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If I dive deep into the depths, the me from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.52,0:45:26.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,is still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.36,0:45:47.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Looking back, there were certainly fragments of dreams sprouting in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.36,0:46:00.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Pressed down by the weight of strings, they eventually turned into hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.24,0:46:08.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There's no use in trying to stroke the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.92,0:46:20.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This small, gentle light... my belief still won't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.92,0:46:33.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even so, I want to draw more of the future with these hands on the white scenery before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.80,0:46:44.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even if the past isn't beautiful, I'll be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.28,0:46:49.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I just want to draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.88,0:46:55.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,this world that reflects in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.57,0:47:04.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}And we're back. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.52,0:47:06.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}My screen just popped up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.56,0:47:15.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}That was the 3DMV for the song Chouchou-P wrote for this event, titled "The Name of Your Drawing."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.24,0:47:21.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Wait, I got mixed up. That was the 3DMV for "The Name of Your Drawing."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.52,0:47:22.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.76,0:47:26.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Should I do this first? Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.36,0:47:32.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}For a second, I thought my own notes were Chouchou-P's comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.44,0:47:33.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I was like, "Wait, what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.20,0:47:33.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.72,0:47:39.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Let me read the notes I sent to the staff beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.24,0:47:40.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.56,0:47:46.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"Just listening to it makes me feel Ena's journey, and it brings me to tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.68,0:47:53.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"The title contains her name, and I felt it was truly a song written for Ena."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.84,0:48:08.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"I sang it with her determination to turn regret and pain into strength, and with the positive feelings she found."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.18,0:48:11.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}That's what past-me emailed to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.64,0:48:16.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Chouchou-P's actual comments were introduced on the ProSeka News Station and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.70,0:48:20.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}They should be on Twitter—I mean, X—as well, so please check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:24.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But yeah, those were the feelings I put into the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.56,0:48:25.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.24,0:48:30.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}There are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.28,0:48:35.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But it's like the current Ena is the one doing the reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.76,0:48:40.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I'm sure Ena has regrets, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.04,0:48:44.66,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But I think she's a girl who understands that those regrets made her who she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.66,0:49:01.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}So even for the phrases about the past, I didn't want to sing them with the pure agony of the old Ena. I sang with my own sense of resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.84,0:49:10.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Like I said during the story part, I tried to include that sense of relief and the brightness of finally understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.80,0:49:15.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But this isn't the goal; it's a new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:24.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I was very conscious of capturing that middle-ground feeling while singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:36.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}So rather than a huge explosion of emotion, it's more like quietly stirring up words within myself to cheer myself on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:40.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Like patting my own chest and saying, "Let's do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.34,0:49:46.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I sang it with that image of self-encouragement in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.32,0:49:48.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I just end up crying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.58,0:49:52.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I've already heard the full version, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.14,0:49:53.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Since I'm the one who sang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.56,0:49:54.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.68,0:49:57.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I just can't help but cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.04,0:49:58.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.82,0:50:02.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Both this story and the song just make me tear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.04,0:50:03.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.72,0:50:06.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't cry this time, either during the talk or the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.50,0:50:07.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But I did anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.06,0:50:08.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.92,0:50:15.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,To those of you who felt a bit jealous that I've heard the full version, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.70,0:50:22.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV for this new song, "The Name of Your Drawing,"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.22,0:50:27.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,will be uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel at 10:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.62,0:50:31.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please check that out along with the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.72,0:50:36.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If it's like the previous 2DMVs, that means you'll be able to hear the full version too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.18,0:50:40.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I haven't even seen the 2DMV myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.60,0:50:52.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, to give some belated thoughts on the 3DMV... I recorded the full song, so I knew how the parts were split.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:54.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I knew which parts would be Ena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.42,0:50:59.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The song starts with the other three members of N25 singing one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.60,0:51:07.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So in the 3DMV inside my head—my imaginary 3DMV—it didn't start with Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.34,0:51:10.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was wondering how it would actually begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.02,0:51:14.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Would all four, or rather five of them appear at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.32,0:51:18.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Or would it start with Mizuki, who has the first line?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.62,0:51:23.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But then I saw jt was showing Ena the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.30,0:51:32.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm always happy when other characters get a lot of screen time for their fans, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.58,0:51:41.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But this MV put such a huge spotlight on Ena, and it matched the story so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.08,0:51:46.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It really felt like it was capturing Ena's way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.32,0:51:51.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As her voice actress, that made me so incredibly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.26,0:52:04.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's always been like this, but Ena's commissioned songs always feel like she's getting closer and closer to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.14,0:52:07.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's just my own otaku analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.26,0:52:08.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But things like that make me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.86,0:52:15.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've only seen it a few times myself, so I want to sit down and watch it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.22,0:52:17.71,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.71,0:52:18.35,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.50,0:52:24.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think that's everything... I don't think I've left anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.46,0:52:29.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Well, I've truly entrusted everything to Ena's voice.
Comment: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:37.78,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:37.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,More than anything, I hope you can feel Ena's way of life through the music and the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.30,0:52:41.66,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please continue to support Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.66,0:52:42.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please keep cheering her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.50,0:52:44.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,To those who already do, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.94,0:52:47.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm not Ena myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.38,0:52:50.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but as the person who voices her,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.72,0:52:55.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm someone close to her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.18,0:53:09.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's made a new resolution, and I'll work hard as an actress to express her growth, so please keep watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.88,0:53:11.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.34,0:53:18.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's been a short time, but that's all for this ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.38,0:53:20.90,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, how did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.46,0:53:28.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished the story for the "Colors of Pure Sense" event yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.00,0:53:31.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Did I look a bit silly crying like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:38.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,You can read the whole thing from the Event Story menu once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.02,0:53:39.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So please, give it a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.60,0:53:43.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We're always looking for messages for AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:51.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,You can submit them through the official ProSeka Discord channel or via email.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.86,0:53:56.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please send one in when the next AfterTalk event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.78,0:54:00.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Just make sure your messages are related to the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.60,0:54:03.71,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste if I couldn't read it because it was about something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.71,0:54:04.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.46,0:54:08.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,In just about ten or twenty seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.18,0:54:12.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,the 2DMV will be out, so let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.94,0:54:18.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll watch it as soon as we close out here, so you should all check it out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.16,0:54:21.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.56,0:54:23.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.48,0:54:40.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.30,0:54:40.95,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That person...
